trans-unit.source: Provides a read-only collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 提供的只读集合<xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref>对象。

trans-unit.source: The TransformerTypeCollection class represents a read-only collection of objects, typically used by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> objects to manage sets of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects.
trans-unit.target: TransformerTypeCollection 类表示的对象，通常由使用的只读集合<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>和<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>对象来管理一组<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>对象。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to keep a list of available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects on a page, whereas a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> object uses a TransformerTypeCollection collection to track the available <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects that it contains.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>控件使用 TransformerTypeCollection 集合要保留的可用的列表<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>对象在页中，而<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone>对象使用 TransformerTypeCollection 集合来跟踪可用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>它所包含的对象。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionsZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Although the TransformerTypeCollection collection is read-only, you can make programmatic changes to the properties of the underlying controls referenced in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 尽管 TransformerTypeCollection 集合是只读的但你可以以编程方式更改集合中引用的基础控件的属性。
